metadata.description: Query Database of SMS, Contacts etc

metadata.cwe: CWE-312: Cleartext Storage of Sensitive Information
metadata.description: Files may contain hardcoded sensitive information like usernames, passwords, keys etc.

metadata.cwe: CWE-649: Reliance on Obfuscation or Encryption of Security-Relevant Inputs without Integrity Checking
metadata.description: The App uses the encryption mode CBC with PKCS5/PKCS7 padding. This configuration is vulnerable to padding oracle attacks.

metadata.cwe: CWE-532: Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File
metadata.description: The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327: Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: MD5 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.
This App uses SQL Cipher. Ensure that secrets are not hardcoded in code.

metadata.cwe: CWE-89: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')
metadata.description: App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.

metadata.cwe: CWE-749: Exposed Dangerous Method or Function
metadata.description: Insecure WebView Implementation. Execution of user controlled code in WebView is a critical Security Hole.
App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.
App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.

metadata.cwe: CWE-330: Use of Insufficiently Random Values
metadata.description: The App uses an insecure Random Number Generator.

playstore_details.title: Capital Rx - Navigate Your Pha
playstore_details.description:
Delivering your pharmacy benefit plan to you, wherever you are.


Navigate your prescription benefit plan quickly and easily. Capital Rx members can search medication history, easily identify in-network pharmacies and lookup pharmacy specific information, all in one place.


Access plan information and health history for you and your family, locate the pharmacy of your choice and check prescription prices – from anywhere!


FIND THE DRUGS YOU NEED AT THE LOWEST PRICES

•	Search for medication prices at retail pharmacies or chosen mail provider
•	Compare prices and to find the lowest cost option near you
•	Search within past claims to find the current price of the drug in the same location
•	Get notified if your medication requires a prior authorization and receive suggested covered alternatives.

LOCATE A PHARMACY NEAR YOU

•	Find pharmacies based on current location or by entering a zip code
•	Easily identify in-network and out-of-network pharmacies
•	Look up hours, languages and services offered

UNDERSTAND YOUR BENEFITS WITH THE CLICK OF A BUTTON

•	Graphical view of Deductible, Out-of-pocket, and Plan spend for individual and family
•	View individual processed claims with payment, drug, and pharmacy information
•	Search for a medication on the formulary or download a PDF 

EASY TO USE DESIGN FOR AN IMPROVED EXPERIENCE

•	Display digital pharmacy ID card easily at the pharmacy
•	Integrated Face ID or Touch ID for quick and secure login
•	Select 'favorite' pharmacies that will always appear at the top of searches 
•	One touch dial to contact customer care team


FOLLOW US
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/cap-rx/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/cap_rx
